ion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4193, \"end\": 4205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999930637387, \"rank\": 6.936369684545584e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4483, \"end\": 4495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999930637387, \"rank\": 6.936369684545584e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 4515, \"end\": 4534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Comcast Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT SPHERE  Sphere is a next-generation entertainment medium that is redefining the future of live entertainment.\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A venue where the foremost artists, creators, and technologists create extraordinary experiences that take storytelling to a new level and transport audiences to places both real and imagined.\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue hosts original Sphere Experiences from leading Hollywood directors; concerts and residencies from the world's biggest artists; and premier marquee events.\", \"